overview:
Panarrow is a Mohali, Punjab based business venture, which came into existence in the year 2010. We are one of the recognized manufacturer and supplier of a wide range of Necklace Sets, Bangles, Bracelets, Designer Bracelets and many more.

Infrastructure: The well furnished infrastructural building of our company addresses to the requirements and needs of our business related processes in an efficient manner.

Our Quality: Being a quality conscious business organization, we aim to deliver only immaculate products to our esteemed clients that are in compliance with set industrial guidelines.

Our Team: We have employed some of the talented and qualified professionals in our team, who enables us to cater to the diverse demands of different clients in an appropriate manner.

Client Satisfaction: Since inception, we focus to render maximum level of satisfaction to our valued clients in every aspect.

Our Products: Necklace Sets Kundan Necklace Sets Traditional Necklace Sets Beaded Necklace Sets Artificial Necklace Sets
